	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />what is the power up state of mmc1 ?
<br />
<br />what does hardware reset do ?
<br />
<br />what reset sets bit 2 and 3 (of 4 - 0)?  is that the reset by writing 0x80 to any register, which resets the serial register ?
<br />
<br />thanks
<br />
<br />matt

		

