	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />In some MMC1 tests I did a while back, I made these two notes:
<br />
<br />- Writing $80 sets bits 2 and 3 of register 0, but doesn't affect anything else.
<br />
<br />- At power-up, register 0 = $0F and the rest have random values (usually $1F).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


